In [4]:
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np

X = np.linspace(-2*np.pi, 2*np.pi, 1000)
y1 = np.sin(X)
y2 = np.cos(X)
y3 = - np.sin(X)
y4 = - np.cos(X)

plt.figure(figsize=(10,6))
plt.plot(X, y1, color='r', linestyle='-', linewidth=2, alpha=0.8)
plt.plot(X, y2, color='b', linestyle='--', linewidth=2)
plt.plot(X, y3, color='g', linestyle='-.', linewidth=2)
plt.plot(X, y4, color='k', linestyle=':', linewidth=2)

plt.show()

绘图样式调整¶

标题(title)、坐标轴标签(label)¶


plt.rcParams['font.sans-serif']=['SimHei']

In [5]:
plt.rcParams['font.sans-serif']=['SimHei'] #
plt.rcParams['axes.unicode_minus']=False #

x = np.linspace(0,5,20)
y1 = x**2
y2 = x**3

plt.figure()
plt.plot(x,y1,'r')
plt.plot(x,y2,'b')

plt.title('Figure', fontsize=16)
plt.xlabel('x', fontsize=14)    # 
plt.ylabel('y', fontsize=14)    #  

plt.show()

In [13]:
x_bar = [10, 20, 30, 40, 50]
y_bar = [0.5, 0.8, 0.4, 0.6, 0.9]

plt.figure(figsize=(6,4))
bars = plt.bar(x_bar, y_bar, color='rygcb', label=x_bar, width=3)
plt.ylim(0.0, 1.0)

for i, rect in enumerate(bars):
    x_test = rect.get_x()
    y_test = rect.get_height() + 0.01
    plt.text(x_test, y_test, '%.1f' % y_bar[i])  # 
    
plt.show()

plt.axis('equal')
plt.show()

In [16]:
x = np.linspace(-5,5,500)
y = np.linspace(-5,5,500)

X, Y = np.meshgrid(x,y)
Z = (1-X/2+X**3+Y**4) * np.exp(-X**2-Y**2)

plt.figure(figsize=(8,8))
plt.contourf(X,Y,Z)
plt.show()

2.7 矩阵热力图¶

In [18]:
M = np.matrix([[1, 0.1, 0.7, 0.6],
              [0.7, 1, 0.5, 0.4],
              [0.4, 0.3, 1, 0.8],
              [0, 0.2, 0.6, 1]])

fig = plt.figure(figsize=(8,6))
ax = fig.add_subplot(111)
cax = ax.matshow(M, vmin=0, vmax=1)

fig.colorbar(cax)
ticks = np.arange(0,9,1)
plt.show()

2.9 子图绘制 subplot¶

In [20]:
x = np.linspace(-2*np.pi, 2*np.pi, 100)

y1 = np.sin(x)
y2 = np.tanh(x)
y3 = np.exp(-(x**2)/2)
y4 = 1/(1+np.exp(-x))

plt.figure(figsize=(12,8))

# 1
plt.subplot(2,2,1)
plt.plot(x, y1, 'r')

# 2
plt.subplot(2,2,2)
plt.plot(x, y2, 'c')

# 3
plt.subplot(2,2,3)
plt.plot(x, y3, 'b')

# 4
plt.subplot(2,2,4)
plt.plot(x, y4, 'g')

plt.show()
In [21]:
fig, axes = plt.subplots(2,2, figsize=(12,8))

axes[0,0].set_title("Figure1")

axes[0,1] = plt.subplot(222)
axes[0,1].set_title("Figure2")
axes[0,1].plot(x, y2, 'c')

axes[1,0] = plt.subplot(223)
axes[1,0].set_title("Figure3")
axes[1,0].plot(x, y3, 'b')

axes[1,1] = plt.subplot(224)
axes[1,1].set_title("Figure4")
axes[1,1].plot(x, y4, 'g')

plt.show()

3. Matplotlib 3D图像绘制¶

  • import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

3.1 三维散点图 scatter¶

In [23]:
import numpy as np

# x, y, z01100
x = np.random.normal(0,1,100)
y = np.random.normal(0,1,100)
z = np.random.normal(0,1,100)

from mpl_toolkits.mplot3d import Axes3D
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

# 3D
fig = plt.figure(figsize=(8,6))
ax = Axes3D(fig)

ax.scatter(x, y, z)
ax.set_xlabel('X Label')
ax.set_ylabel('Y Label')
ax.set_zlabel('Z Label')

plt.show()

3.3 三维曲面图 plot_surface¶

In [25]:
# 3D
fig = plt.figure(figsize=(8,6))
ax = Axes3D(fig)

X = np.arange(-2,2,0.1)
Y = np.arange(-2,2,0.1)
X, Y = np.meshgrid(X,Y)
Z = np.sqrt(X**2+Y**2)

# cmap
ax.plot_surface(X, Y, Z, cmap=plt.cm.winter)
ax.set_xlabel('X Label')
ax.set_ylabel('Y Label')
ax.set_zlabel('Z Label')

plt.show()

3.5 三维子图绘制¶

In [27]:
# 1
fig = plt.figure(figsize=(12,5))

# 1
ax1 = fig.add_subplot(1, 2, 1, projection='3d')

x = np.linspace(-6*np.pi,6*np.pi, 1000)
y = np.sin(x)
z = np.cos(x)

ax1.plot(x, y, z)

# 2
ax2 = fig.add_subplot(1, 2, 2, projection='3d')

X = np.arange(-2, 2, 0.1)
Y = np.arange(-2, 2, 0.1)
X, Y = np.meshgrid(X, Y)
Z = X**2-Y**2

ax2.plot_surface(X, Y, Z, cmap=plt.cm.autumn)

plt.show()
